            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink-500">Ottimizzato + RAG</div>
            <pre class="mt-2 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded bg-ink-900/[0.04] p-3 font-mono text-xs text-ink-700 dark:bg-white/[0.04] dark:text-ink-300">ANSWER: CHF 10 miliardi
SOURCE: FINMA-RS 2010/01 Rz 6</pre>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-swiss">Supera</p>
          </div>
